{
  "texts": [
    "To sum up, our contributions are the following:• We introduce the novel idea of using LLMs to compare alternative smart-home XAR methods generating natural language explanations, with the goal of selecting the best one.",
    "• We propose two different prompting strategies to evaluate explanations.",
    "• Our preliminary results suggest that both prompting strategies are aligned with user surveys.",
    "EVALUATING EXPLANATIONS USING LLMS 2.1 Problem Formulation and Research Question2.1.1 Problem Formulation.",
    "Consider a smart-home that is equipped with several environmental sensors (e.g., motion sensors, magnetic sensors, pressure sensors)."
  ]
}